org.gvsig.tools.dynobject

Interface DynField

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DynField_LabelAttribute, DynField_v2, DynFormFieldDefinition, EditableFeatureAttributeDescriptor, FeatureAttributeDescriptor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDynField, DefaultDynFormFieldDefinition, DefaultEditableFeatureAttributeDescriptor, DefaultFeatureAttributeDescriptor, DynFieldFacadeOfAFeatureAttributeDescriptor

    public interface DynField
extends Cloneable
    A field of a DynObject.

    A field will be persisted only if it is set as persistent (@see isPersistent(), which is the default value.
